00:40:42.640 --> 00:40:54.680
" I'll tell you where you'll be in the next couple of years by who you're hanging around, what books you're reading, what you're watching on TV, and what you're meditating on.

00:40:54.680 --> 00:41:01.040
You must come up higher in your walk with the Father in 2026.

00:41:01.040 --> 00:41:12.360
But I bring all this to you because it's what has helped me, and so people are always asking.

